# Student Registration System (Full Stack)

This project implements a simple **Student Registration System** using:

- Frontend: HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript  
- Backend: Node.js with Express  
- Database: MySQL  
- API Style: REST (JSON)

The application allows users to **register students** and **retrieve registered student data**.

